name: Sunlight Dancer Garment
description: Inspired by the underwater life, this garment represents the natural sensuality and freedom of Brazilian Carnival. If chosen, its daylight will guide you.  This is one of the two pieces of a digital fashion collab with @pedrobbrasil. There are 20 pieces of each garment, minted half at my account and half at his. Go get yours! Soundtrack by @rhz
